All Implemented Interfaces:
Configurable, java.util.Observer
public class NSGA2ObjectiveValuesStatisticsLogTool
extends NSGA2LogTool

This logtool logs in every generation the minimum, maximun, mean and standard deviation of each objective of the Pareto-front and the whole current population. Use only with NSGA2Algorithm.

IMPORTANT: It is asumed that all objectives are minimized.

Author:
rafa
